###  ::before 

css 

```css
.parent {
    position: fixed;
    display: block;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    text-align: center;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, .5);
}
.parent :before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: middle;
    height: 100%;
}

.parent .child {
    display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: middle;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    line-height: 60px;
    color: red;
    background: yellow;
}
```

